            "type": "text",
            "text": "Strategies to Reduce Chatterbox Cost"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implement caching for repeated queries to minimize token usage. Use batch processing for non-real-time requests to leverage volume discounts. Optimize prompt length by removing redundant context without sacrificing accuracy. Set rate limits per endpoint to prevent unexpected spikes in Chatterbox cost."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Real-Time Monitoring and Alerts"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrate cost tracking tools like cloud billing APIs or custom dashboards to visualize Chatterbox cost trends. Configure alerts for threshold breaches, such as daily spend exceeding $50. Analyze usage patterns weekly to adjust quotas and identify cost-saving opportunities."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Advanced Optimization Techniques"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Leverage model distillation or fine-tuning to reduce token requirements for specific tasks. Implement fallback mechanisms to cheaper models for low-priority requests. Regularly audit API calls for unused features that contribute to Chatterbox cost, and refactor code to eliminate them."
          }
        ]
      }
